  11:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + Peripheral Control functions
  12:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + Peripheral State functions
  13:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *
