 830:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   * @note  You can use SubSeconds and SecondFraction (sTime structure fields
 831:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *        returned) to convert SubSeconds value in second fraction ratio with
 832:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *        time unit following generic formula:
 833:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *        Second fraction ratio * time_unit =
