1697:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   * @brief  Waits until the RTC Time and Date registers (RTC_TR and RTC_DR) are
1698:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *         synchronized with RTC APB clock.
